ygData.messageBody:
I just found out about this site, so I love it. I
am a level 12 Barbarian Warrior, and I have been
playing since the first game game out. (March 99, I
think. =´┐¢) I know, ONLY levl. 12? I always switch chars.
so, I play as this one for a while. I am currently in
GFay, hunting in CB, throne group room. my name is
Victria. I am an ADDICT! I play for at least35+ hours a
week, if there's not a patch... and that's only in 5
dayas. I play on Karana. contact me. I like giveing
newbie stuff to newbies. it is fun. Bye bye
